General.Name: ASN Broker Public Company Limited
General.Description: ASN Broker Public Company Limited, together with its subsidiaries, provides insurance brokerage services in Thailand. It operates through three segments: Insurance Broker, Loan, and Peer-to-Peer. The company offers non-life insurance and life insurance broker services; lending services through the peer-to-peer lending platform; and personal loans. ASN Broker Public Company Limited was founded in 2005 and is based in Bangkok, Thailand.
